Title: The Contest
Plot: George's mother throws her back out when she falls down after catching him doing "you know." When George says he'll never do it again, Jerry challenges him to a contest of self-denial, when he accepts, Elaine and Kramer want in on the action, or rather the lack of it.
GuestStars: Jane Leeves, Estelle Harris, Ilana Levine, Rachel Sweet, Andrea Parker
